      "header": "Emphasis: Proportion (Principle)",
      "content": [
        {
          "params": {
            "text": "<p>The 'Where Winds Meet' feature uses proportion to show importance. It is significantly larger than the 'Now Available' thumbnails on the right, signaling that it is the primary featured product.</p>"
